{"id":"shethar-boznai","term":"Shethar-boznai","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Star of splendour, a Persian officer who vainly attempted to hinder the rebuilding of the temple (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 5:3\">Ezra 5:3</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 1:6\">6</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 6:6\">6:6</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 6:13\">13</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Ezra 5:3","Genesis 1:6","Genesis 6:6","Genesis 6:13"]}